{"blogid": "125120675", "writerAge": "码龄3年", "writerBlogNum": "37", "writerCollect": "84", "writerComment": "7", "writerFan": "13", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "629", "writerName": "无情大菜刀", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_125120675.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "39479", "writerRankWeekly": "367253", "writerThumb": "22", "writerVisitNum": "34876", "blog_read_count": "895", "blog_time": "于 2022-06-04 22:12:21 发布", "blog_title": "C#上位机基础知识", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<p>注意:框架.NFT版本选择，4.5版本只能用在win7系统及以上<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0ebf229948214ff19a0bd1b896ef5370.png\"/><br/> 给应用APP更改图标，图标文件只能是.ico文件，可以通过在线转换器将图片转换成.ico文件。http://www.51tool.com/ico/?action=make<img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\cd135b0ec761441395dfa069f5c39420.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\339baef41148424eb4effee3d82caa1b.png\"/><br/> 组件选择串口<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ab3a7d17113640ce872d3e4f38c89a02.png\"/><br/> 在bin文件夹里把应用.exe文件发送给其他电脑后就可以用了。直接复制出来就可以用了。<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a3020df4052e4c6ebd87bfa167e07076.png\"/></p>\n<p>做上位机<br/> 一. 常用的控件：<br/> 1.Form -窗体<br/> 2.Label -标签<br/> 3.Button -按键<br/> 4.RadioButton -单选+Panel -面板<br/> 5.CheckBox -多选框<br/> 6.ComboBox -下拉选项<br/> 7.TextBox -文本框<br/> 8.PictruBox -图片框<br/> 9.ProgressBar -进度条<br/> 10.GroupBox -组合框（把一类的东西放在一个框里）</p>\n<p>二. 常用组件：<br/> 1.Timer -定时器<br/> 2.SerialPout -串口</p>\n<p>Form 设置，打开时候的在屏幕的位置显示<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3eb379824ee144f1a6f6ebac545111f9.png\"/><br/> 窗口最大，最小化设置<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a725528353d349fa890c11ae4dd19451.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\cbfa67d79acc4bef9178285ee76bbb1d.png\"/><br/> 2.标签<br/> 用于简单介绍<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\06f0f07fd4b5448ba98bc11b5b7f3fba.png\"/><br/> 3.按键<br/> 双击按键，进入代码编辑<br/> 显示文本<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\5abcc43108af48d3bf6a17f417697851.png\"/><br/> 添加文本<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\7e331b00bbc245b985c3f77f0847aeeb.png\"/><br/> 按钮添加标志位<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b163b54eef6e46eaa3eddc62c6bece94.png\"/><br/> 字符判断，加按键字类容改变<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\974082c7be7a455e811ada210ed9700b.png\"/></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">  private void button2_Click<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>object sender, EventArgs e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>button2.Tag.ToString<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"off\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                button2.Tag <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"on\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                button2.Text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"暂停\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                button2.Tag <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"off\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                button2.Text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"播放\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>效果<img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6023d10d2fe042798f3593086cf20e4b.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c615dc0a46434c3c9946b1f980fa2f9d.png\"/><br/> 按键换肤</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">   button2.BackgroundImage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Properties.Resources.Image_CloseSerial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   button2.Tag <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"OFF\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>4.单选框（多和容器使用Panel）<br/> 只能选中一个<br/> 容器的外观设置<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\236e89bd6dcd4b229aefd1d6a8c19786.png\"/><br/> 代码应用和多选框类似</p>\n<p>5.多选框<br/> 把多选框当作全局标志位使用</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"> private void button1_Click<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>object sender, EventArgs e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>checkBox1.Checked <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                textBox1.AppendText<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"确认\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//添加文本\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                textBox1.AppendText<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"否认\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//添加文本\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>效果<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b27a2bc412b0446c8ad0f5b900a23b52.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\f448952b69904988a14c8b94ec67a23e.png\"/></p>\n<p>6.下拉选项<br/> 组合框选择的内容<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\499c04f498ae4c5689a66d80d522b76f.png\"/><br/> 禁止输入，只可选择<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\bdadb5adfb5d46e580dd144968084697.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\32fb3ab8c68044e5ae596a179afff6a1.png\"/><br/> 7.文本框<br/> 显示多行<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\487698c884c14634bb0860b98add6e31.png\"/><br/> 添加滚动条，查看所有信息<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\bce22be25c4c433aa22f201fb792ee5a.png\"/><br/> 8.图片组合框<br/> 添加资源，为后面的图片显示提供图片<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\aa9513cd64c94aeba134b557d488d30e.png\"/></p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\"> //在代码中更换图片\n pictureBox1.Image <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Properties.Resources._8463505<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//_8463505是图片名称\n</code></pre>\n<p>9.进度条设置<br/> 代码<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6a040840e1bb4c609c884a48a33bd099.png\"/><br/> 二.组件<br/> 1.定时器</p>\n<p>给图片添加Tag值<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\73b87f120ce04932bbd184e646a6c80c.png\"/><br/> 切换图片</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">        private void timer1_Tick<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>object sender, EventArgs e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pictureBox1.Tag.ToString<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                pictureBox1.Tag <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                pictureBox1.Image <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Properties.Resources.娱乐APP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pictureBox1.Tag.ToString<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n                pictureBox1.Tag <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                pictureBox1.Image <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Properties.Resources._8463505<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-bash\">timer1.Stop<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//定时器停止\ntimer1.Start<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//定时器开始\n</code></pre>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "C#", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 1, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-06-04 22:12:21", "summary": "注意框架版本选择，版本只能用在系统及以上在这里插入图片描述给应用更改图标，图标文件只能是文件，可以通过在线转换器将图片转换成文件。在这里插入图片描述在这里插入图片描述组件选择串口在这里插入图片描述在文"}